    <title>New Features and Developments</title>

    <para>
        <emphasis role="strong">ITE performance improvements</emphasis>
    </para>
    <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                Completeness check operations within the ITE, that are
                supposed to ensure the projects executable consistency,
                are now performed in the background and do no longer
                cause the UI from being blocked.
            </para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
